A utility to split a given file into a series of chunks, compress and encrypt those chunks and allow the user to
pass a handler to upload them, or save to disk, or what have you.

Provides the facility to decrypt, decompress, and rejoin those chunks back into the original file.

Version 1.0

8-08-14:
    v1.0: Feature-complete. Javadocs in process. See test/ukumo/decoupled/me/ukumo/TestMain.java for usage example.

25-07-14:
    v.12: Added ChunkIterator to define how chunks are found and presented to the Joiner.

25-07-14
    v0.1: split->compress and decompress->join implemented. hooks provided for encryption interfaces.
